      "cookedHtml": "<p><strong>Ask <a href=\"http://monday.com\">monday.com</a>’s co-founders’ your burning questions!!</strong><br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/c/c9d016b44ff483abbcf844efa31d93b80c122a24.png\" title=\"Roy Mann\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/c/c9d016b44ff483abbcf844efa31d93b80c122a24_2_250x250.png\" alt=\"Roy Mann\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">Roy Mann</span><span class=\"informations\">600×600 127 KB</span>\n</div></a></div> <div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/1/1b8c9fcca79bf233817a4dc5a5df6909e0523e5c.png\" title=\"Eran Zinman\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/1/1b8c9fcca79bf233817a4dc5a5df6909e0523e5c_2_250x250.png\" alt=\"Eran Zinman\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">Eran Zinman</span><span class=\"informations\">600×600 134 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>Our annual conference, Elevate, is fast approaching and we’re really looking forward to sharing the jam-packed 2 day event with you!</p>\n<p>On day 1 of the conference, September 15th, at 1:30pm - 2:00pm PDT (US Elevate) // September 22nd, at 2:30pm - 3:00pm GMT+2 (EU Elevate), we will host a unique  <strong>“Ask Us Anything”</strong> session with Roy Mann (<a href=\"http://monday.com/\">monday.com</a> CEO) and Eran Zinman (<a href=\"http://monday.com\">monday.com</a>) CTO). We still have some spots for questions during this session - the power is in your hands!</p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://forms.monday.com/forms/f42ef5196586af10faadf8c6d9a64360\">Ask a Question</a></strong></p>\n<p>We will collect questions by the end of this week - so make sure to submit yours now!If you haven’t already registered for your spot at Elevate, <a href=\"https://www.elevatebymonday.com/agenda\">register now.</a></p>"
